test.doc: End-to-End test of the complete flow in the Amazon clone app. This test covers the main interactions of both Admin and User: 1. Admin registers a new product in the "Electronics" category with the name "Xbox Series X" 2. User creates a new account and logs into the app. 3. User adds the product to the cart. 4. User completes the purchase and verifies the order. 5. Admin logs into the app again. 6. Admin checks the orders made by the customer.
